                                    </visa-and-health>
                                    <div class="base-model__body-inner-footer">
                                        
<p class="MsoNormal"><strong>Travel Guidelines by Destination</strong></p>
<p class="MsoNormal">To board your flight, you must meet the entry requirements for all countries on your itinerary, including transit and final destinations. Pay attention to recent travel history regulations.</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">Stay updated with the latest guidelines from governments and airlines to ensure a smooth journey. Plan ahead and comply with all travel regulations to avoid disruptions.</p>
<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>
